# STM32CubeIDE outputs
**/Debug/
**/Release/

# Keep EMWaver's canonical STM32 make build dirs in-repo (used by `emwaver build`).
!emwaver-firmware/Debug/
!emwaver-firmware/Debug/**
!emwaver-firmware/Release/
!emwaver-firmware/Release/**

# STM32CubeMX-generated vendor middleware (ST SLA0044; regenerate via .ioc)
emwaver-*-firmware/Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Device_Library/

# Eclipse / CubeIDE metadata
**/.settings/
**/.metadata/
